title: POWERTRIP_What_is_paintball_DVDR_ENGSUB
description:
This is the instructional DVD that paintball team Powertrip from Sweden made because we were tired of answering the same question over and over about what paintball is.

It&#039;s a few years old so you might find it a little bit dated regarding equipment and 
such, but the basics of the game are still the same if you try to explain to someone that doesn&#039;t know about paintball.

This is a complete ISO of the DVD, mount it or burn it to DVD and enjoy. If you Don&#039;t like the subtitles you can turn them off, sorry English isn&#039;t my native language.

# Jon
